													"type": 22,
													"value": "CinematicNodeContext"
												},
												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "[Start of Line]: Player passes object to Dammon. He inspects it (only if we can convey this without showing the object since design needs to be able to iterate it)\r\n\r\n[End of Line]: Dammon turns to his forging equipment and does some, uh, general forging. Shouldn't show weapon specifically and can be handled with a generic.\r\n(CINEMATIC DUPE OF N115)"
												}
